{"tid":2454046,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃國健：新制度下選出的議員能夠更穩定支持政府","createTime":"2021-03-20T02:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T03:23:04.000Z","uid":278587,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a5965f59466a0526fd35e1b134662093ea341b2d","tid":2454046,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T02:37:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=428103\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D428103&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDD1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=e80de8b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D428103&h=37c30ed3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=428103</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】全國人大常委將會修改香港選舉制度，立法會議席增至90席，選委會議席可能佔較大比例，有立法會議員認為新制度下選出的議員能夠更穩定支持政府，但有議員就擔心新議員只會盲目支持政府。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員（九龍東）黃國健：「要落實行政主導，他需要有一批議員較穩定地支持政府，選委會選出的新議員可能就承擔這個責任。」<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員（紡織及製衣界）鍾國斌：「很多時候政府提交的議案、法案，我們往往看到有很大問題，我們會強力要求修改，或我們修改，如果新的議員有五、六十位，對運作未純熟，可能有時局長打電話去幫幫忙支持，他們收到局長電話就支持便糟糕了。」"},{"pid":"07a22b988edb0130ba5fc4f18caabf69634ee1f0","tid":2454046,"uid":72633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T02:39:02.000Z","msg":"自由黨要被滅黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae67a10699143b833c3c0f30769af4936f2608be","tid":2454046,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T02:39:40.000Z","msg":"新制度下選出的<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">忠誠廢物</span></span></strong>議員能夠更穩定支持<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">忠誠廢物</span></span></strong>政府"},{"pid":"45cde440a76c2f4846c829a20f6f5d65915cebd6","tid":2454046,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T02:41:45.000Z","msg":"忠誠廢物思維永遠係咁<br />\n<br />\n咁仲使乜立法會<br />\n等你地鳩噏一輪再舉手仲冇效率<br />\n最後又係老共話事，港共執行"},{"pid":"7ab42d3197f